   email triggered emails https://litmus.com/blog/?p=11799 <p>We asked 20
   experts for their predictions about email marketing in 2020. In this
   SlideShare, weôve selected our favorite prediction from each of our 20
   contributors, and made it easy for you to tweet the ones you find
   intriguing or agree with. Enjoy this peek at the future of email
