   rel="nofollow" href="https://litmus.com/blog">Litmus Blog</a>.</p>
   <p>úHow will email marketing change by the end of the decade?ù</p>
   <p>Thatôs the question we posed to 20 experts for our <a
   href="https://litmus.com/lp/email-marketing-in-2020?utm_campaign=email2
   020&#038;utm_source=slideshare&#038;utm_medium=social">Email Marketing
   in 2020</a> report. Their answers predict dramatic changes in
   personalization, automation, interactivity, compliance, and much
   more.</p> <p>In this SlideShare, weôve selected our favorite prediction
   from each of our 20 contributors, and made it easy for you to tweet the
   ones you find intriguing or agree with. Enjoy this peek at the future
   of email marketing!</p> <p><iframe
   src="//www.slideshare.net/slideshow/embed_code/key/eIkCFZiEEyQoof"
